{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1724335539.25368", "card_id": "Q_664869379", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 405}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何理解《黑神话：悟空》第一章结尾观音所说「若不披上这件衣裳，众生又怎知我尘缘已断、金海尽干」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "若不披上这件衣裳，众生又怎知我尘缘已断、金海尽干"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0932a97ba35e1aef24470f0a906ca6cc_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "875 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664869379"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIjcCNlKOkybJBEAMaCTExMDAyNjI0MiD7l5W2BjAAOIoHQAByCTY2NDg2OTM3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1724335539.26173", "card_id": "Q_664992869", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《文明 7》Steam 已开始预售，其中购买 448 元的豪华版可以提前 5 天开始游戏，你会现在就下单么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "《文明 7》已正式开启预售，并公布了售价和相关游戏信息。 这款游戏在国区的售价为 298 元，另外还有豪华版和奠基者版可供选择，豪华版售价 448 元，奠基者版售价 558 元。 豪华版包括完整的基础游戏、提前体验（最早可在 2025 年 2 月 6 日游玩）、特库姆塞与肖尼族包以及世界歧路合集，其中包含了 2 名新领袖、 4 个新文明、 4 个新奇观和 1 个特殊外观奖励等发布后的内容；豪华内容包中包含 2 个领袖形象、 4 个档案自定义项和 1 个探路者备选皮肤。 而奠基者版除了拥有豪华版的所有内容外，还额外赠送了《统治权力合集》，其中包括 4 个新文明、 1 个战争迷雾地块组合和奠基者宫殿皮肤等发布后的内容。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-d0a110014c586082c3f89ef22d89c4ed_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "360 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664992869"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIjcCNlKOkybJBEAMaCTExMDA1MzY3NiDoupu2BjAAOOIBQAFyCTY2NDk5Mjg2OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1724335539.26994", "card_id": "Q_664987950", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 21}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待我国科学家发现一种用月壤产水的方法？是否有实用前景？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "科研人员发现，月壤矿物储存了大量氢。在加热至高温后，氢将与矿物中的铁氧化物发生氧化还原反应，生成单质铁和大量水。当温度升高至 1000℃以上时，月壤会熔化，反应生成的水将以水蒸气的方式释放。经分析计算，1 吨月壤将可产生约 51-76 千克水，相当于 100 多瓶 500 毫升的水。更多资讯请下载央视新闻客户端"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3a388e3b21af878307c1eb59410cd02a_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "95 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664987950"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IjcCNlKOkybJBEAMaCTExMDA1MjU5MSDujZu2BjAAOCRAAnIJNjY0OTg3OTUweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1724335539.27692", "card_id": "Q_664893150", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 92}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "《黑神话：悟空》杨戬以反派形象登场，明明有很多正面经历为什么他在影视、游戏和文学方面总以反派身份出现？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4eef7a141ac4d8961b5fa69f4fa4f1f4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "91 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/664893150"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIjcCNlKOkybJBEAMaCTExMDAzMTU4MCCzx5a2BjAAOLwBQANyCTY2NDg5MzE1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1724335539.27914", "card_id": "Q_664989510", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon